law.history: Repealed 2014 Ky. Acts ch. 22, sec. 26, effective July 15, 2014. -- Repealed, reenacted, renumbered, and amended 2013 Ky. Acts ch. 121, sec. 18, effective June 25, 2013. -- Amended 2012 Ky. Acts ch. 125, sec. 2, effective July 12, 2012. -- Created 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 432, sec. 8, effective June 17, 1978.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Restrictions on issuance of NQ2 retail drink licenses to certain restaurants or hotel dining facilities.
